### Test API Endpoints
### Install VS Code Extension: "REST Client" by Huachao Mao
### Then click "Send Request" above each request

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:4000/health

### 2. Login (Get Access Token)
### REPLACE with your actual email and password!
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "your-email@example.com",
  "password": "your-password"
}

### 3. Test Google API (Admin only)
### REPLACE YOUR_TOKEN_HERE with the token from login response!
GET http://localhost:4000/admin/test/google-api
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. Import Sample POIs (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:4000/admin/test/import-sample
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Get POI Statistics
GET http://localhost:4000/admin/pois/stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 6. Get My Profile
GET http://localhost:4000/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. List Challenges
GET http://localhost:4000/challenges

### 8. List Challenges by Region
GET http://localhost:4000/challenges?region=VIC

